1
00:00:07,958 --> 00:00:08,791
[CROWD chatter]

2
00:00:08,875 --> 00:00:09,958
[footsteps approaching]

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,791
[BOTH singing] C is ‘cause
they’re super cute.

4
00:00:14,875 --> 00:00:17,208
O is like
their perfect shape.

5
00:00:17,291 --> 00:00:18,583
What song
are you singing?

6
00:00:18,666 --> 00:00:20,541
This is our
new Cookie Song!

7
00:00:20,625 --> 00:00:23,708
[singing]
K is better than cake!

8
00:00:23,791 --> 00:00:25,583
[TAKUMA]
Doesn’t Cake start with a C?

9
00:00:25,666 --> 00:00:29,125
E’s the way
that "cookie" ends.

10
00:00:29,208 --> 00:00:34,125
[SHERA and KREBSKULM]
Let’s all sing it again.

11
00:00:34,208 --> 00:00:35,916
Let’s hear
the folks in the back!

12
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,541
Uh, what?

13
00:00:37,625 --> 00:00:40,916
[KREBSKULM singing] C is ‘cause
they’re super cute!

14
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,375
O is like
their perfect shape!

15
00:00:44,458 --> 00:00:49,041
[singing bleakly]
K is better than cake.

16
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:53,708
[SHERA and KREBSKULM]
E’s the way that "cookie" ends!

17
00:00:53,791 --> 00:00:57,500
Let’s all sing it again.

18
00:00:57,583 --> 00:00:58,875
[KREBSKULM]
Come on, you know the words!

19
00:00:58,958 --> 00:01:00,375
[SHERA laughing]

20
00:01:00,458 --> 00:01:05,541
♪

21
00:02:30,416 --> 00:02:32,875
♪

22
00:02:32,958 --> 00:02:34,458
[KREBSKULM]
So good!

23
00:02:34,541 --> 00:02:37,833
I can’t get enough
of these in my face!

24
00:02:37,916 --> 00:02:38,708
[KREBSKULM chews]

25
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:41,708
[sighs happily]
Yum!

26
00:02:41,791 --> 00:02:43,291
[slurps]
This dirty water’s

27
00:02:43,375 --> 00:02:45,541
bitter and disgusting!

28
00:02:45,625 --> 00:02:48,041
Here.
Try some of this.

29
00:02:48,125 --> 00:02:49,416
It’s hot chocolate.

30
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,083
[KREBSKULM]
Interesting.

31
00:02:51,166 --> 00:02:53,083
[KREBSKULM slurps]

32
00:02:53,166 --> 00:02:55,541
I assume you’ve heard
about all this?

33
00:02:55,625 --> 00:02:58,708
Klem is the Demon Lord.
Without a memory.

34
00:02:58,791 --> 00:03:00,250
What do you
make of it?

35
00:03:00,333 --> 00:03:01,750
Hmm.

36
00:03:01,833 --> 00:03:03,666
Of her being
the Demon Lord?

37
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,708
Or obsessing
over cookies?

38
00:03:05,791 --> 00:03:07,000
Just be glad
she’s not trying to

39
00:03:07,083 --> 00:03:08,375
kill the mortal races.

40
00:03:08,458 --> 00:03:09,708
Oh.

41
00:03:09,791 --> 00:03:11,916
[CELES]
I’m only here out of curiosity.

42
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,416
I had to see
this dichotomy for myself.

43
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,666
I think for now,
we just sit back and wait.

44
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,250
See how it plays.

45
00:03:18,333 --> 00:03:20,791
Congratulations,
Rem, on freedom.

46
00:03:20,875 --> 00:03:22,000
Yeah.

47
00:03:22,083 --> 00:03:23,625
Thanks for your help, Celes,

48
00:03:23,708 --> 00:03:25,625
I know how much stress
I’ve caused you.

49
00:03:25,708 --> 00:03:26,958
[CELES chuckles]

50
00:03:27,958 --> 00:03:28,833
[door bell jingles]

51
00:03:28,916 --> 00:03:31,000
[SHERA]
Best snacks ever!

52
00:03:31,083 --> 00:03:32,958
[KREBSKULM]
Let’s come here every day!

53
00:03:33,041 --> 00:03:34,458
Amazing how understanding

54
00:03:34,541 --> 00:03:36,458
Celes was
about everything.

55
00:03:36,541 --> 00:03:37,750
[SHERA]
I’m glad she knows

56
00:03:37,833 --> 00:03:39,958
Klem would never do
anything to hurt us.

57
00:03:40,041 --> 00:03:41,000
Me too.

58
00:03:41,083 --> 00:03:42,208
[DIABLO]
She had to be thorough

59
00:03:42,291 --> 00:03:43,958
in her investigation, though.

60
00:03:44,041 --> 00:03:45,250
Since she’s
the one protecting

61
00:03:45,333 --> 00:03:46,500
the barrier of Faltra,

62
00:03:46,583 --> 00:03:48,250
she’s not allowed
to leave the city.

63
00:03:48,333 --> 00:03:49,416
She didn’t
want anyone else

64
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,708
to suffer that
fate unnecessarily.

65
00:03:51,791 --> 00:03:52,833
[DIABLO]
At least now Rem won’t

66
00:03:52,916 --> 00:03:54,083
have to lose her freedom.

67
00:03:54,166 --> 00:03:56,166
I’m so happy
for you, Rem, Rem?

68
00:03:57,958 --> 00:03:59,125
[SHERA]
They were right behind us

69
00:03:59,208 --> 00:04:00,500
a second ago.

70
00:04:00,583 --> 00:04:01,541
[grunts]

71
00:04:01,625 --> 00:04:03,708
♪

72
00:04:05,166 --> 00:04:06,458
What’s with the alley?

73
00:04:06,541 --> 00:04:08,125
I’m not that kind of cat.

74
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:10,250
Do Shera and Diablo
know where we are?

75
00:04:10,333 --> 00:04:12,125
♪

76
00:04:12,208 --> 00:04:13,208
[ALICIA]
They don’t.

77
00:04:13,291 --> 00:04:15,208
I’d only
planned to bring Klem.

78
00:04:15,291 --> 00:04:17,041
I figured I’d
bring Shera later

79
00:04:17,125 --> 00:04:18,541
when the time was right.

80
00:04:18,625 --> 00:04:22,333
Then I realized,
it doesn’t really matter.

81
00:04:22,416 --> 00:04:24,416
I’m not as
certain as I thought

82
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,583
about who
might be the key.

83
00:04:26,666 --> 00:04:27,583
Okay?

84
00:04:27,666 --> 00:04:29,250
[door creaks open]

85
00:04:30,291 --> 00:04:31,541
Nobody’s here.

86
00:04:31,625 --> 00:04:33,000
I’ll go look.

87
00:04:33,083 --> 00:04:34,541
You stay here and wait.

88
00:04:34,625 --> 00:04:36,833
They may still come back.

89
00:04:36,916 --> 00:04:38,000
Right.

90
00:04:38,083 --> 00:04:41,208
♪

91
00:04:43,208 --> 00:04:45,083
[TAKUMA]
My chest is pounding.

92
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:46,875
I wonder what that means.

93
00:04:46,958 --> 00:04:49,041
Do you have any idea
what could possibly

94
00:04:49,125 --> 00:04:51,208
be causing the loss
of your memories?

95
00:04:51,291 --> 00:04:53,875
[KREBSKULM] If I did,
I probably forgot.

96
00:04:53,958 --> 00:04:55,666
[ALICIA] It’s just that
one of the Fallen priests

97
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:57,708
said it takes more
than just magic power

98
00:04:57,791 --> 00:05:00,750
to completely
resurrect a Demon Lord.

99
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:02,333
A Fallen?

100
00:05:02,416 --> 00:05:03,375
[ALICIA]
I want to find out

101
00:05:03,458 --> 00:05:05,041
how to restore
your memories,

102
00:05:05,125 --> 00:05:07,791
so that we might awaken the
Demon Lord and her bloodlust.

103
00:05:07,875 --> 00:05:09,000
[REM]
Okay, time out!

104
00:05:09,083 --> 00:05:10,333
I thought I just
heard you say

105
00:05:10,416 --> 00:05:12,166
you wanted the Demon Lord
to fully resurrect

106
00:05:12,250 --> 00:05:15,166
so that she can kill
all of the mortal races?

107
00:05:15,250 --> 00:05:17,375
Your hearing appears
to be in good shape.

108
00:05:17,458 --> 00:05:18,458
You are correct.

109
00:05:18,541 --> 00:05:19,583
[REM gasps]

110
00:05:19,666 --> 00:05:21,916
What the hell is
wrong with you?

111
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,166
[ALICIA]
Nothing.

112
00:05:23,250 --> 00:05:25,166
I’m the same
as I’ve always been.

113
00:05:25,250 --> 00:05:27,416
Except.
I don’t need to pretend

114
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:28,583
we’re all friends anymore,

115
00:05:28,666 --> 00:05:29,750
thank goodness.

116
00:05:29,833 --> 00:05:31,958
That got old
really quickly.

117
00:05:32,041 --> 00:05:33,583
[KREBSKULM]
If anyone needs to wake up,

118
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:35,125
it’s you,
Lady Knight!

119
00:05:35,208 --> 00:05:36,708
I couldn’t be
more perfectly

120
00:05:36,791 --> 00:05:39,208
and completely
resurrected if I tried.

121
00:05:39,291 --> 00:05:41,625
Yet, you’re refusing
to kill the mortal races?

122
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:43,666
That’s enough!
You want me to burn you?

123
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:44,875
-[ALICIA] Yes!
-[KREBSKULM whimpers]

124
00:05:44,958 --> 00:05:46,583
If that’s what it takes

125
00:05:46,666 --> 00:05:48,333
to awaken my lord, please do!

126
00:05:48,416 --> 00:05:50,958
What an absolute blessing
that would be.

127
00:05:51,041 --> 00:05:52,791
If I could become
the first mortal

128
00:05:52,875 --> 00:05:54,083
who was burned to death,

129
00:05:54,166 --> 00:05:55,875
I would help make
this world beautiful

130
00:05:55,958 --> 00:05:59,250
by dying along with
the rest of the races!

131
00:05:59,333 --> 00:06:01,125
What the crap?

132
00:06:01,208 --> 00:06:02,291
[REM]
So the woman Galluk

133
00:06:02,375 --> 00:06:03,916
was screaming
about that one time?

134
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,583
[GALLUK] I should’ve
listened to that woman

135
00:06:05,666 --> 00:06:07,166
when I had the chance!

136
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:08,750
Who do you mean?

137
00:06:08,833 --> 00:06:10,541
Yes, that was me.

138
00:06:10,625 --> 00:06:12,500
I was doing my best
to lead him.

139
00:06:12,583 --> 00:06:14,500
I even handed him
Gregore disguised

140
00:06:14,583 --> 00:06:15,625
as his sword.

141
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:16,875
[scoffs]

142
00:06:16,958 --> 00:06:18,333
[ALICIA]
He was a handful, wasn’t he?

143
00:06:18,416 --> 00:06:20,625
Pathetic, dramatic,
and teeming with envy

144
00:06:20,708 --> 00:06:21,958
and hatred,

145
00:06:22,041 --> 00:06:24,541
just like the rest
of those hideous mortals.

146
00:06:25,833 --> 00:06:28,375
[SADDLER]
We finally found you.

147
00:06:28,458 --> 00:06:29,583
I’ve been
searching for you

148
00:06:29,666 --> 00:06:32,375
for quite some
time, Lady Cristela.

149
00:06:32,458 --> 00:06:33,583
You again?

150
00:06:33,666 --> 00:06:35,375
I apologize, Sir.

151
00:06:35,458 --> 00:06:37,500
As you see,
I’ve been a little tied up,

152
00:06:37,583 --> 00:06:39,625
trying to reform
these Demon Lord Worshipers.

153
00:06:39,708 --> 00:06:40,833
[scoffs]

154
00:06:40,916 --> 00:06:42,375
You said you
wanted her to burn you!

155
00:06:42,458 --> 00:06:43,750
Oh, no!

156
00:06:43,833 --> 00:06:45,916
She’s trying to
control my mind again.

157
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,666
I went undercover
to expose them

158
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,875
as Demon Lord worshipers,
and it worked!

159
00:06:49,958 --> 00:06:51,333
At least
I saved this child

160
00:06:51,416 --> 00:06:52,958
they kidnapped
from her family!

161
00:06:53,041 --> 00:06:54,958
So that’s the yarn
you’re spinning now?

162
00:06:56,291 --> 00:06:58,666
This news comes
as no surprise to us.

163
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,333
I’ve suspected
that your souls

164
00:07:00,416 --> 00:07:01,958
were dark all along.

165
00:07:02,041 --> 00:07:03,000
What’s the deal?

166
00:07:03,083 --> 00:07:04,500
I thought
you were a rock?

167
00:07:04,583 --> 00:07:05,958
[SADDLER]
Oh, that.

168
00:07:06,041 --> 00:07:08,250
I’ve never known
such a disgrace.

169
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:09,791
To think that anyone
would do something

170
00:07:09,875 --> 00:07:11,416
so insolent to me,

171
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:14,416
one with power
granted by the Gods.

172
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:15,750
Make no mistake,

173
00:07:15,833 --> 00:07:18,125
he will be punished
for that in due time.

174
00:07:18,208 --> 00:07:20,791
Come forth, Asulau!
[yelps]

175
00:07:22,041 --> 00:07:23,125
[ALICIA scoffs]

176
00:07:23,208 --> 00:07:24,708
[growls]

177
00:07:24,791 --> 00:07:26,416
Go on!
Hurry it up.

178
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:27,833
Break through them!

179
00:07:27,916 --> 00:07:30,166
Form a shield, men!

180
00:07:30,250 --> 00:07:31,333
[gasps]

181
00:07:31,416 --> 00:07:33,708
[men scream]

182
00:07:33,791 --> 00:07:35,083
What the hell
kind of idiots

183
00:07:35,166 --> 00:07:36,166
would do that?

184
00:07:36,250 --> 00:07:37,583
Are they trying
to get killed?

185
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:39,375
Our lives in this world
are only worth

186
00:07:39,458 --> 00:07:42,000
as much as the Gods
have need for us.

187
00:07:42,083 --> 00:07:44,250
Death is
a great opportunity.

188
00:07:44,333 --> 00:07:46,708
It simply means we’ve
been invited into Heaven.

189
00:07:47,958 --> 00:07:49,458
[grunts]

190
00:07:49,541 --> 00:07:51,333
[blood splashes]

191
00:07:51,416 --> 00:07:53,458
[SADDLER]
Most importantly, protecting me

192
00:07:53,541 --> 00:07:56,083
is the equivalent
to protecting a God.

193
00:07:56,166 --> 00:07:57,375
[ASULAU'S body thuds]

194
00:07:57,458 --> 00:07:58,791
[SADDLER]
Cowards who refuse to obey

195
00:07:58,875 --> 00:08:01,083
my orders out of fear
for their own lives,

196
00:08:01,166 --> 00:08:02,833
could never
become squires.

197
00:08:06,541 --> 00:08:08,625
♪

198
00:08:08,708 --> 00:08:09,666
[gasps]

199
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,333
[yells]

200
00:08:11,416 --> 00:08:12,833
[grunts]

201
00:08:12,916 --> 00:08:15,208
Now the power
of the Gods compels you!

202
00:08:15,291 --> 00:08:17,833
Bow down before us,
Demon Lord Worshiper!

203
00:08:17,916 --> 00:08:19,583
[REM gagging]

204
00:08:19,666 --> 00:08:21,541
Hey! Stop that!

205
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:24,125
[gagging]

206
00:08:26,416 --> 00:08:28,250
The only thing she needs

207
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:30,583
is to feel true hatred.

208
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:35,291
[CROWD chatter]

209
00:08:37,458 --> 00:08:38,583
[panting]

210
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,541
[TAKUMA]
Damn it!

211
00:08:41,625 --> 00:08:43,208
Can’t help but think
something’s screwy!

212
00:08:43,291 --> 00:08:45,625
Better not be some
instinctual warning about

213
00:08:45,708 --> 00:08:46,958
anything.

214
00:08:47,041 --> 00:08:47,958
[grunts]

215
00:08:49,083 --> 00:08:52,291
[echoing]
Hey! Hey. Hey!

216
00:08:52,375 --> 00:08:54,458
Are you awake?

217
00:08:54,541 --> 00:08:55,791
[exhales softly]

218
00:08:55,875 --> 00:08:57,000
[gasps]

219
00:08:57,083 --> 00:08:59,166
What’s going on?
Are you all right?

220
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:00,541
Where are we?

221
00:09:00,625 --> 00:09:01,958
I can’t tell you
how hard it is

222
00:09:02,041 --> 00:09:03,208
to look at your
face after you lost

223
00:09:03,291 --> 00:09:05,208
such a lame battle.

224
00:09:05,291 --> 00:09:07,750
Here.
Eat this, it’ll help.

225
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:09,458
Thanks, I’m starving.

226
00:09:09,541 --> 00:09:11,916
I love these.

227
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,333
[KREBSKULM]
Is it true you’ve been sad

228
00:09:13,416 --> 00:09:15,125
for a long time
because of me?

229
00:09:15,208 --> 00:09:16,708
[gasps]

230
00:09:16,791 --> 00:09:19,208
Alicia was talking about it.

231
00:09:19,291 --> 00:09:21,000
[KREBSKULM] She said
your life’s basically sucked

232
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:22,291
and it’s my fault.

233
00:09:22,375 --> 00:09:24,250
And that your mother,
and her mother,

234
00:09:24,333 --> 00:09:26,958
and her mother’s mother
were also suffering.

235
00:09:27,041 --> 00:09:28,500
[REM]
Well...

236
00:09:28,583 --> 00:09:31,041
[KREBSKULM]
But you still tried to save me.

237
00:09:31,125 --> 00:09:32,125
And you did
the same thing

238
00:09:32,208 --> 00:09:34,000
with Eulerex, too.

239
00:09:34,083 --> 00:09:35,666
I gotta say,
if there was an award

240
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:37,375
for loyalty,
it would be all yours,

241
00:09:37,458 --> 00:09:38,708
Rem-gnat!

242
00:09:38,791 --> 00:09:40,708
[REM]
It wasn’t out of loyalty.

243
00:09:40,791 --> 00:09:42,041
[gasps softly]

244
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:44,083
I don’t understand it, either.

245
00:09:44,166 --> 00:09:45,750
I, uh...

246
00:09:45,833 --> 00:09:47,833
I’ve spent
my whole life hating you.

247
00:09:47,916 --> 00:09:49,500
At least, what I thought
was the Demon Lord,

248
00:09:49,583 --> 00:09:51,125
Krebskulm.

249
00:09:51,208 --> 00:09:52,750
I gave up on my dreams,

250
00:09:52,833 --> 00:09:54,958
and I pushed people away.

251
00:09:55,041 --> 00:09:58,416
I lived my entire life
in fear and isolation.

252
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:00,375
What the hell’s wrong with me?

253
00:10:00,458 --> 00:10:01,583
[REM]
I mean, my enemy is sitting

254
00:10:01,666 --> 00:10:03,041
right in front of my face,

255
00:10:03,125 --> 00:10:05,583
but I can’t bring myself
to wish you were gone.

256
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:08,583
I’m sorry, Rem.

257
00:10:08,666 --> 00:10:11,458
I forced you to
live your life as a prisoner.

258
00:10:11,541 --> 00:10:12,666
[gasps]

259
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,833
[KREBSKULM]
You should allow yourself

260
00:10:13,916 --> 00:10:15,583
to hate me,
it’s only natural.

261
00:10:17,083 --> 00:10:21,291
Life without
freedom is not life.

262
00:10:21,375 --> 00:10:23,166
[REM] You would know
after being trapped

263
00:10:23,250 --> 00:10:25,458
for the same amount
of time my family was.

264
00:10:25,541 --> 00:10:27,541
For several generations.

265
00:10:27,625 --> 00:10:30,041
That’s a long time
to be alone in the dark.

266
00:10:30,125 --> 00:10:32,916
Nah, it felt more like
a really long nap.

267
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,291
[REM]
Was becoming a Demon Lord

268
00:10:34,375 --> 00:10:36,708
the only reason you were
imprisoned within us?

269
00:10:37,875 --> 00:10:39,500
[KREBSKULM]
Yeah, but it’s how I was born.

270
00:10:39,583 --> 00:10:41,333
Not what I chose.

271
00:10:41,416 --> 00:10:42,750
I understand.

272
00:10:42,833 --> 00:10:45,958
I think you and I
are a lot alike in that way.

273
00:10:46,041 --> 00:10:47,416
[KREBSKULM]
We are?

274
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:50,166
Yes and that’s why
we need to stick together.

275
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:53,166
I’m not gonna let
Alicia have her way.

276
00:10:53,250 --> 00:10:54,666
Yeah! Neither am I!

277
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:56,541
I’m fine just like I am!

278
00:10:56,625 --> 00:10:58,583
Look at me
and tell me I’m not perfect,

279
00:10:58,666 --> 00:11:00,250
am I right?

280
00:11:00,333 --> 00:11:01,666
[chuckles softly]

281
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,750
Let’s get back before
the others freak out.

282
00:11:03,833 --> 00:11:05,875
I don’t think you know
how ridiculously quick

283
00:11:05,958 --> 00:11:07,166
we’d be out of here
if I was allowed

284
00:11:07,250 --> 00:11:08,666
to use my powers.

285
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:10,625
Those mean canned soldiers
would be ash right now.

286
00:11:10,708 --> 00:11:11,958
Just saying.

287
00:11:12,041 --> 00:11:14,500
[REM]
I get it, but hold back.

288
00:11:14,583 --> 00:11:15,833
I’m kinda into the Klem

289
00:11:15,916 --> 00:11:17,791
that makes up
food songs with Shera,

290
00:11:17,875 --> 00:11:21,416
laughs at anything,
and obsesses over cookies.

291
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,208
[REM]
Don’t ever lose that.

292
00:11:23,291 --> 00:11:24,625
Don’t let your
heart become numb

293
00:11:24,708 --> 00:11:26,500
to killing mortal races.

294
00:11:26,583 --> 00:11:29,500
Promise me you’ll stay true
to who you are now.

295
00:11:29,583 --> 00:11:31,458
Wow, that’s
a lot to take in.

296
00:11:31,541 --> 00:11:33,125
But I promise you, Rem!

297
00:11:33,208 --> 00:11:34,208
[chuckles softly]

298
00:11:34,291 --> 00:11:36,125
[horse neighs]

299
00:11:36,208 --> 00:11:38,125
Good news,
we’re finally here.

300
00:11:38,208 --> 00:11:41,000
You’ll soon be saved
from your demonic desires.

301
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:49,750
♪

302
00:11:49,833 --> 00:11:50,958
[door creaks open]

303
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,875
-[shudders]
-[PALADIN 1] Move.

304
00:11:55,958 --> 00:11:57,500
[footsteps approaching]

305
00:11:57,583 --> 00:12:00,500
♪

306
00:12:00,583 --> 00:12:01,458
[gasps]

307
00:12:02,416 --> 00:12:04,708
Seriously?
I’m no Demon Lord worshiper!

308
00:12:04,791 --> 00:12:06,583
And I’m not gonna lie
and say that I am

309
00:12:06,666 --> 00:12:08,583
even if you torture me!

310
00:12:08,666 --> 00:12:10,583
[SADDLER]
I appreciate that.

311
00:12:10,666 --> 00:12:12,250
Usually anyone who’s heard

312
00:12:12,333 --> 00:12:14,000
the rumors about me
starts spewing

313
00:12:14,083 --> 00:12:15,708
shallow
vows of repentance

314
00:12:15,791 --> 00:12:17,500
the second
they see my tools.

315
00:12:17,583 --> 00:12:18,833
Of course.

316
00:12:18,916 --> 00:12:22,041
I can always see
right through their charade.

317
00:12:22,125 --> 00:12:23,500
You don’t fool me.

318
00:12:23,583 --> 00:12:26,083
I know the signs of a true
Demon Lord worshiper,

319
00:12:26,166 --> 00:12:28,750
and you’re trying to
deceive the holy ones.

320
00:12:28,833 --> 00:12:30,500
You don’t care
what I have to say,

321
00:12:30,583 --> 00:12:32,041
you just wanna torture me.

322
00:12:32,125 --> 00:12:34,458
I’m offering you
your salvation.

323
00:12:34,541 --> 00:12:36,750
All I want is to cleanse
your tainted soul

324
00:12:36,833 --> 00:12:38,333
and release you into Heaven.

325
00:12:38,416 --> 00:12:39,958
Don’t you want to be free?

326
00:12:40,041 --> 00:12:43,166
Gimme a break. Like you’re
a god now or something?

327
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:45,166
[SADDLER]
Not "or something."

328
00:12:45,250 --> 00:12:47,125
That’s exactly what I am.

329
00:12:47,208 --> 00:12:49,708
A living god who
just wants to save you.

330
00:12:50,666 --> 00:12:53,041
[SADDLER] I was born
into a blessed family,

331
00:12:53,125 --> 00:12:54,458
granted a blessed body,

332
00:12:54,541 --> 00:12:57,083
and I boast
a blessed intellect.

333
00:12:57,166 --> 00:12:58,583
What other explanation

334
00:12:58,666 --> 00:13:01,416
could there possibly be
than that I am a God

335
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:03,000
who has descended
from Heaven

336
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:04,333
to save the world?

337
00:13:04,416 --> 00:13:06,250
[grunts]
Why don’t you save the world

338
00:13:06,333 --> 00:13:07,833
from your ass-face?

339
00:13:07,916 --> 00:13:09,750
[SADDLER]
Those ears of yours.

340
00:13:09,833 --> 00:13:11,000
They’re made from evil.

341
00:13:11,083 --> 00:13:12,416
[gasps]

342
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:14,916
[SADDLER] That tail
isn’t very pure either.

343
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,416
And those hands
were used to

344
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:18,875
cast a wicked
Summon at me.

345
00:13:18,958 --> 00:13:21,083
You’re judging me now?
Go to hell!

346
00:13:21,166 --> 00:13:23,583
Seems your
mouth is evil too.

347
00:13:23,666 --> 00:13:25,750
Perhaps we should
extract your tongue.

348
00:13:25,833 --> 00:13:26,958
[REM]
Alicia!

349
00:13:27,041 --> 00:13:28,041
Are you really
just going to

350
00:13:28,125 --> 00:13:29,208
stand there
like a scared goat

351
00:13:29,291 --> 00:13:30,625
and let them
threaten me this way?

352
00:13:30,708 --> 00:13:32,708
What kind of
two-faced monster are you?

353
00:13:32,791 --> 00:13:36,083
I have my own
missions to accomplish.

354
00:13:36,166 --> 00:13:37,916
But if you don’t like pain,

355
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,166
perhaps you should ask
your friend for help?

356
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:41,333
[gasps]

357
00:13:41,416 --> 00:13:42,958
Rem, you know
I can stop them now

358
00:13:43,041 --> 00:13:44,333
if you need me to.

359
00:13:44,416 --> 00:13:45,625
I don’t need it, Klem.

360
00:13:45,708 --> 00:13:47,125
Do you understand?

361
00:13:47,208 --> 00:13:48,500
Please keep your promise!

362
00:13:48,583 --> 00:13:50,583
I... I will.

363
00:13:50,666 --> 00:13:52,041
[REM]
This “mission” you have

364
00:13:52,125 --> 00:13:54,416
is to resurrect
the Demon Lord, isn’t it?

365
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:57,666
You want her to wipe
out the mortal races!

366
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:59,125
The Demon Lord Worshiper

367
00:13:59,208 --> 00:14:01,375
is trying to poison my mind
with her intentions.

368
00:14:01,458 --> 00:14:03,791
You made me like you,
you tin-nipped botch!

369
00:14:03,875 --> 00:14:06,041
And you went with us
to rescue Shera!

370
00:14:06,125 --> 00:14:08,333
[REM] You’re saying
that meant nothing?

371
00:14:11,625 --> 00:14:12,791
[ALICIA]
Lord Saddler,

372
00:14:12,875 --> 00:14:15,416
may I leave this
in your hands?

373
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:17,833
Yes. It would be my honor.

374
00:14:19,291 --> 00:14:21,875
[REM]
Oh, hell no. Alicia!

375
00:14:21,958 --> 00:14:23,583
[doors shut]

376
00:14:23,666 --> 00:14:25,125
[REM whimpering]

377
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:26,500
Now, then.

378
00:14:27,458 --> 00:14:29,625
Shall we get things started?

379
00:14:29,708 --> 00:14:31,416
[footsteps approaching]

380
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,750
[panting]

381
00:14:36,166 --> 00:14:37,625
-[sighs] Damn it!
-[BAR CROWD chatter]

382
00:14:37,708 --> 00:14:39,333
I’ve looked
everywhere for them.

383
00:14:39,416 --> 00:14:40,875
I need a guide or something.

384
00:14:40,958 --> 00:14:42,166
Any kind of clue.

385
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:44,000
[DWARF 1] You want
a piece of me now, punk?

386
00:14:44,083 --> 00:14:45,625
[DWARF 2] Had a piece
of your mom last night,

387
00:14:45,708 --> 00:14:46,958
smell my breath!

388
00:14:47,041 --> 00:14:48,083
[DWARF 1]
You think that’s funny...

389
00:14:48,166 --> 00:14:50,125
[DIABLO grunts]
That’s right!

390
00:14:50,208 --> 00:14:51,375
After that,

391
00:14:51,458 --> 00:14:53,208
I was surrounded
by hundreds of scoundrels

392
00:14:53,291 --> 00:14:54,625
and took them out one by one!

393
00:14:54,708 --> 00:14:56,166
-[door opens forcibly]
-Huh?

394
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:57,416
[pants]

395
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:00,166
There she is.

396
00:15:00,250 --> 00:15:02,625
What’s with this
scorned look, my friend?

397
00:15:02,708 --> 00:15:05,000
You two!
[grunts]

398
00:15:05,083 --> 00:15:06,208
[EMILE]
Hmm?

399
00:15:06,291 --> 00:15:07,458
[TAKUMA]
No, wait.

400
00:15:07,541 --> 00:15:09,666
How does a Demon Lord
ask for a favor?

401
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:11,958
All I’ve ever done
is order people around.

402
00:15:12,041 --> 00:15:13,250
And even without social skills

403
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:14,666
I know that’s not
a productive way

404
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,625
to ask for stuff.

405
00:15:16,708 --> 00:15:19,000
If I were them
and I came at me like this,

406
00:15:19,083 --> 00:15:20,416
I’d tell me to eff off.

407
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:23,041
So how do I
tone it down, though?

408
00:15:23,125 --> 00:15:24,166
[DIABLO]
You see...

409
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:27,833
[stammers]
Rem and, uh, Klem are...

410
00:15:27,916 --> 00:15:28,750
[blows raspberry]

411
00:15:28,833 --> 00:15:30,333
[DIABLO]
Uh, uh...

412
00:15:30,416 --> 00:15:31,708
[EMILE]
Huh?

413
00:15:31,791 --> 00:15:33,458
[TAKUMA stammers]
French Roast!

414
00:15:33,541 --> 00:15:35,666
Why can’t I just,
just talk without

415
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:37,125
snarling through everything?

416
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:39,666
Use your words.

417
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,750
[EMILE]
Where’s our confidence

418
00:15:40,833 --> 00:15:42,833
hiding tonight, hmm?

419
00:15:42,916 --> 00:15:44,458
[gasps]

420
00:15:44,541 --> 00:15:45,666
[BOY 1]
Guildmaster!

421
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,583
Serious junk
is going down!

422
00:15:47,666 --> 00:15:49,041
My friend said
he just saw a Paladin

423
00:15:49,125 --> 00:15:50,416
carrying Rem somewhere!

424
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,083
-Huh?
-The fair maiden!

425
00:15:52,166 --> 00:15:53,916
Do you know
if it’s just Rem?

426
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,125
-Huh?
-Anyone else with her?

427
00:15:56,208 --> 00:15:59,000
[BOY 1] He said there was
some little girl with her.

428
00:15:59,083 --> 00:16:00,041
[BOY 1]
They went in the church

429
00:16:00,125 --> 00:16:01,541
in the North District!

430
00:16:01,625 --> 00:16:03,375
[grunts]
Thank you!

431
00:16:03,458 --> 00:16:04,583
Huh?

432
00:16:05,916 --> 00:16:08,166
Did I just hear him
say thank you?

433
00:16:08,250 --> 00:16:11,500
No, you heard him
scream thank you.

434
00:16:11,583 --> 00:16:12,833
[BOTH chuckle]

435
00:16:12,916 --> 00:16:14,416
[EMILE]
Well, I can’t just sit here!

436
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:16,458
Rem is in distress
and needs a rescue!

437
00:16:16,541 --> 00:16:17,666
[SYLVIE]
Go get her!

438
00:16:17,750 --> 00:16:19,750
[DIABLO]
I have to make it in time!

439
00:16:19,833 --> 00:16:21,541
♪

440
00:16:24,166 --> 00:16:25,125
[GALFORD]
What?

441
00:16:25,208 --> 00:16:27,958
They’re all Fallen, you say?

442
00:16:28,041 --> 00:16:30,500
Send message
to Lady Baudelaire at once!

443
00:16:30,583 --> 00:16:32,750
Tell her to secure
the barrier quickly!

444
00:16:32,833 --> 00:16:33,916
[SOLDIER 1]
Yes, sir!

445
00:16:35,625 --> 00:16:37,833
And what, pray tell,
is happening here?

446
00:16:37,916 --> 00:16:38,791
[rumbling]

447
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:44,458
♪

448
00:16:47,625 --> 00:16:50,583
Stay away.
They must not enter Faltra.

449
00:16:50,666 --> 00:16:53,500
This barrier
shall remain protected.

450
00:16:56,875 --> 00:16:58,083
[SADDLER]
Feel free to scream

451
00:16:58,166 --> 00:17:00,250
as much as you’d like.

452
00:17:00,333 --> 00:17:01,541
No one will hear you,

453
00:17:01,625 --> 00:17:03,416
but it might be
fun, nonetheless.

454
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:04,875
Be fun to see me in pain?

455
00:17:04,958 --> 00:17:06,666
Did you sell your conscience
on the dwarf market?

456
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:08,333
Of course not.

457
00:17:08,416 --> 00:17:11,000
It hurts to see
Demon Lord worshipers,

458
00:17:11,083 --> 00:17:13,083
who need salvation.

459
00:17:13,166 --> 00:17:14,791
[whimpers]

460
00:17:14,875 --> 00:17:16,458
-[PALADIN 1] Hold still!
-[cries]

461
00:17:16,541 --> 00:17:17,500
That’s it!

462
00:17:17,583 --> 00:17:18,708
-[REM] No!
-[gasps]

463
00:17:18,791 --> 00:17:20,625
You promised me, remember?

464
00:17:20,708 --> 00:17:23,250
-Stay back!
-[KREBSKULM] But, why?

465
00:17:23,333 --> 00:17:24,583
[pained whimpers]

466
00:17:24,666 --> 00:17:27,541
♪

467
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:29,791
Hmm.
[chuckles]

468
00:17:29,875 --> 00:17:32,000
And that’s why
he told you to sit still!

469
00:17:32,083 --> 00:17:33,291
[grunts]

470
00:17:33,375 --> 00:17:34,583
[gasps]

471
00:17:34,666 --> 00:17:35,750
[gasps]

472
00:17:35,833 --> 00:17:37,083
Rem, no!

473
00:17:37,166 --> 00:17:38,000
[KREBSKULM]
Why do you want me

474
00:17:38,083 --> 00:17:39,250
to let them hurt you?

475
00:17:39,333 --> 00:17:42,125
Let me kill them!
Just say it’s okay!

476
00:17:42,208 --> 00:17:43,791
[REM groans]
Don't.

477
00:17:43,875 --> 00:17:45,500
I don’t want you to die!

478
00:17:45,583 --> 00:17:47,166
[KREBSKULM grunts]

479
00:17:47,250 --> 00:17:48,125
[SADDLER chuckles]

480
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:50,833
If you dare to interfere,

481
00:17:50,916 --> 00:17:52,125
I’ll show you no mercy,

482
00:17:52,208 --> 00:17:53,833
even if you are a child.

483
00:17:53,916 --> 00:17:54,875
[scoffs]

484
00:17:54,958 --> 00:17:57,375
♪

485
00:17:57,458 --> 00:17:58,666
[growls softly]

486
00:17:59,666 --> 00:18:00,625
[BOTH grunt]

487
00:18:00,708 --> 00:18:01,791
[grunts]

488
00:18:01,875 --> 00:18:04,250
[PALADIN 2 gasps]
She’s a Fallen!

489
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:06,250
Take one step toward her,

490
00:18:06,333 --> 00:18:07,875
I’ll turn you to ash.

491
00:18:07,958 --> 00:18:10,083
[SADDLER scoffs]
Damn Fallen.

492
00:18:10,166 --> 00:18:12,125
Pretending to be
a human child.

493
00:18:12,208 --> 00:18:13,583
How repulsive!

494
00:18:13,666 --> 00:18:15,416
You’ll all pay for what
you’ve done to Rem.

495
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:18,291
It’ll cost each one of you
your pathetic lives!

496
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:20,750
[SADDLER]
Shut your fallen brat mouth.

497
00:18:20,833 --> 00:18:21,791
[straining grunts]

498
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:24,916
[REM gasps]

499
00:18:34,833 --> 00:18:37,041
[KREBSKULM]
Rem! Rem?

500
00:18:37,125 --> 00:18:40,791
Oh, Rem! Hey!
Talk to me, please!

501
00:18:40,875 --> 00:18:43,541
Go. Run away.

502
00:18:43,625 --> 00:18:45,875
I won’t!
Not without you!

503
00:18:45,958 --> 00:18:48,916
I’m gonna kill these men
and take you with me!

504
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:51,500
-[REM] You promised me.
-[gasps]

505
00:18:51,583 --> 00:18:53,625
Yeah but, that was before.

506
00:18:53,708 --> 00:18:54,833
[whimpers]

507
00:18:54,916 --> 00:18:56,500
♪

508
00:18:56,583 --> 00:18:58,625
Another damn demihuman.

509
00:18:58,708 --> 00:19:00,541
You’re in the way!

510
00:19:00,625 --> 00:19:02,500
[SADDLER grunting]

511
00:19:02,583 --> 00:19:06,875
♪

512
00:19:08,583 --> 00:19:10,250
[KREBSKULM whimpers]

513
00:19:10,333 --> 00:19:13,750
♪

514
00:19:13,833 --> 00:19:15,000
[KREBSKULM gasping]

515
00:19:17,875 --> 00:19:19,083
[screams]

516
00:19:23,458 --> 00:19:24,416
What the hell?

517
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:26,083
[KREBSKULM screaming]

518
00:19:30,791 --> 00:19:31,791
[REM]
That’s it.

519
00:19:33,166 --> 00:19:34,958
That’s what she meant.

520
00:19:36,916 --> 00:19:38,541
The only thing she needs

521
00:19:38,625 --> 00:19:40,708
is to feel true hatred.

522
00:19:40,791 --> 00:19:43,166
[REM]
It’s because of me.

523
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:44,416
[screaming]

524
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:46,958
[REM]
I’m so sorry, Klem.

525
00:19:47,041 --> 00:19:48,000
[roaring]

526
00:19:49,125 --> 00:19:52,083
♪

527
00:19:52,166 --> 00:19:55,291
[ALICIA]
Finally, the true resurrection.

528
00:19:55,375 --> 00:19:57,333
All the horrible mortal races

529
00:19:57,416 --> 00:19:59,416
will soon be gone!

530
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:00,958
But how?

531
00:20:01,041 --> 00:20:02,875
-That’s impossible!
-[growling]

532
00:20:02,958 --> 00:20:06,291
[SADDLER]
The Demon Lord has resurrected?

533
00:20:06,375 --> 00:20:07,833
[roars]

534
00:20:12,791 --> 00:20:14,541
[SADDLER]
I am not afraid of you!

535
00:20:14,625 --> 00:20:15,583
I’ll destroy you using

536
00:20:15,666 --> 00:20:16,916
all the powers of the gods

537
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,333
that I command!

538
00:20:19,708 --> 00:20:20,916
You cannot harm me,

539
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,083
for I am
a living god myself!

540
00:20:23,166 --> 00:20:25,458
Kneel before me, Demon,

541
00:20:25,541 --> 00:20:27,666
and let me see you suffer!

542
00:20:29,625 --> 00:20:30,500
[grunts]

543
00:20:32,916 --> 00:20:34,541
[SADDLER]
My-- my eyes!

544
00:20:34,625 --> 00:20:36,083
[PALADIN 1]
Lord Saddler?

545
00:20:36,166 --> 00:20:41,375
[pained groans]
No. No way. It can’t be!

546
00:20:41,458 --> 00:20:42,875
[SADDLER]
Does this mean

547
00:20:42,958 --> 00:20:44,416
I’m not really a god?

548
00:20:55,666 --> 00:20:56,458
[gasps]

549
00:20:56,541 --> 00:20:57,375
[gasps]

550
00:20:57,458 --> 00:20:58,416
[ALL gasp]

551
00:20:58,500 --> 00:20:59,541
[grunts]

552
00:20:59,625 --> 00:21:01,083
[DIABLO]
Am I too late?

553
00:21:01,166 --> 00:21:04,541
♪

554
00:21:16,833 --> 00:21:18,666
[DIABLO grunts]

555
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,000
It’s you!

556
00:21:20,083 --> 00:21:21,666
[SHERA]
Diablo!

557
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:22,708
[SHERA panting]

558
00:21:22,791 --> 00:21:25,125
Shera?
What are you doing here?

559
00:21:25,208 --> 00:21:27,916
I used Turkey Shot
to look for everyone,

560
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,291
and I saw Rem!

561
00:21:29,375 --> 00:21:31,500
She’s there.
She’s hurt!

562
00:21:33,916 --> 00:21:35,833
[DIABLO]
What do you mean she’s hurt?

563
00:21:35,916 --> 00:21:36,875
Where’s Alicia?

564
00:21:36,958 --> 00:21:38,416
[SHERA]
I don’t know!

565
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:40,791
[DIABLO]
I see.

566
00:21:40,875 --> 00:21:42,708
Take these.

567
00:21:42,791 --> 00:21:44,583
I’m going to hold Klem back.

568
00:21:44,666 --> 00:21:47,208
It’s going to be up
to you to save Rem.

569
00:21:47,291 --> 00:21:51,083
All right.
Please don’t get hurt,

570
00:21:51,166 --> 00:21:54,541
and please,
please say you’ll save Klem!

571
00:21:54,625 --> 00:21:57,250
[DIABLO]
Shera, do you know who I am?

572
00:21:57,333 --> 00:21:58,958
[DIABLO]
I am the true Demon Lord

573
00:21:59,041 --> 00:22:00,833
who was summoned
from another world!

574
00:22:02,208 --> 00:22:04,083
You have nothing
to worry about!

575
00:22:04,166 --> 00:22:06,916
If anyone can handle this,
it’s me!

576
00:23:38,166 --> 00:23:39,541
[SHERA]
You can’t die Rem!

577
00:23:39,625 --> 00:23:41,166
Not here!
Please!

578
00:23:41,250 --> 00:23:43,916
[DIABLO] This attack
should wake you up, Klem!

579
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:45,916
[REM]
Let’s go home, Klem.

